taramea
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:speargrass (espec. <i>Aciphylla squarrosa</i>); also called spaniard, spear-grass, bayonet-grass the larger of two related varieties of spear-grass. [Maori]
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
